text: Camila Benedicto (born 7 December 1977) is a Brazilian equestrian. She competed in two events at the 2008 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Brazil Category:Equestrians at the 2008 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from São Paulo
